======================================================================

python-pypdf2 (Python library for manipulating pages of PDF files)

A pure-python PDF library capable of splitting, merging, cropping,
and transforming the pages of PDF files.
It can also add custom data, viewing options, and passwords to PDF
files. pypdf can retrieve text and metadata from PDFs as well.

HOME: https://github.com/py-pdf/PyPDF2

======================================================================
REQUIRES: python-cryptography 

